info.name: Test REST API MS-Task
info.description:
Common methods for _**CRUD**_ applications.

- First method: getting all products from the database.
    
- Second method: getting one product by ID.
    
- Third method: adding a new product. Data is in the body.
    
- Fourth method: changing an existing product by ID. Data is in the body.
    
- Fifth method: deleting a product by ID.
